Requires [tasmota32-lvgl.bin](http://ota.tasmota.com/tasmota32/release/tasmota32-lvgl.bin) firmware.

Fully supported with all sensors and SD card.

For configuration, use the "Configuration" - "Auto-configuration", select "M5Stack Tough" and apply. 